commit.message: Add new changelog file formatted in Markdown

Makefile: install compatibility with OSX/BSD

The `-D` option is not available in the BSD version of `install`.
Add DragonFly to default device names

Add support for DragonFly

Fix output on OSX, and use raw disk device.
Add '--help' and '--version' options to the manpage
Use EXIT_FAILURE instead of '1' for exit() argument
Release 'drive' file handle as soon as possible
Make it possible to prevent stripping e.g. with STRIP=/bin/true.
Mention Hurd's default CD-ROM device name
Add comment to the patch by Samuel Thibault
